des:
Challenge Alexa in this fun game of Rock, Paper and Scissors and make it your favorite pass time. This skill maintains user stats and these can be queried by asking Alexa for the same.

Rules - 
1. Paper covers rock
2. Rock destroys scissor
3. Scissor cuts paper

Can you beat an AI like Alexa and master this game?
